  "texts": [
    "XSL • FO RenderXAll experiments were carried out in different system settings.",
    "All GPT-3.5 experiments were conducted using the GPT-3.5 Turbo application programming interface as of the September 2023 update.",
    "The LLaMA-2 model was directly accessed for our experiments.",
    "Gemini was accessed using the Gemini application (previously BARD)-Google's generative artificial intelligence conversational system.",
    "These varied system settings and access methods were taken into account to ensure the reliability and validity of our experimental results, given the differing architectures and capabilities of each LLM.In evaluating the prompt-based approaches on GPT-3.5, Gemini, and LLaMA-2, we have also incorporated traditional NLP baselines to provide a comprehensive understanding of the LLMs' performance in a broader context."
